description: This is a market on whether Magnus Carlsen will win the Goldmoney Asian Rapid, scheduled to take place from June 26, 2021 to July 4, 2021. This market will resolve to “Yes” if Magnus Carlsen wins the Goldmoney Asian Rapid, and “No” otherwise. If the Goldmoney Asian Rapid is rescheduled to an end date on or before July 15, 2021, the same market conditions will apply. If the Goldmoney Asian Rapid is rescheduled to an end date after July 15, 2021, the market will resolve 50-50. More information can be found here: https://championschesstour.com/. In the event of ambiguity in terms of the market outcome, the market will be resolved at the sole discretion of the Markets Integrity Committee (MIC).
